query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(k mk t) NoHashJoin(k mk t cc) NoHashJoin(cc k mk t mc) NoHashJoin(cc k mc mk t cct2) NoHashJoin(cc cct2 k mc mk t mi) NoHashJoin(cc cct2 k mc mi mk t ci) NoHashJoin(cc cct2 ci k mc mi mk t it) NoHashJoin(cc cct2 ci it k mc mi mk t cct1) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 ci it k mc mi mk n t an) NoHashJoin(an cc cct1 cct2 ci it k mc mi mk n t cn) NoHashJoin(an cc cct1 cct2 ci cn it k mc mi mk n t chn) NoHashJoin(an cc cct1 cct2 chn ci cn it k mc mi mk n t rt) NoMergeJoin(an cc cct1 cct2 chn ci cn it k mc mi mk n rt t pi) NoHashJoin(an cc cct1 cct2 chn ci cn it k mc mi mk n pi rt t it3) */ select count(*)
from keyword AS k
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.title = 'Shrek 2' AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994 AND 2002
inner join complete_cast AS cc
on t.id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct2
on cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.info like 'USA:%200%'
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
'(voice) (uncredited)',
'(voice: English version)')
inner join info_type AS it
on it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates'
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct1
on cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
inner join name AS n
on n.id = ci.person_id AND n.name like '%An%' AND n.gender = 'f'
inner join aka_name AS an
on n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
inner join company_name AS cn
on cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
inner join char_name AS chn
on chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name = 'Queen'
inner join role_type AS rt
on rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress'
inner join person_info AS pi
on n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id
inner join info_type AS it3
on it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND it3.info = 'height';
